## Non-Commercial / Open Source Use

For non-commercial use, educational purposes, personal projects, or open source projects,
this software is licensed under the GNU General Public License v3.0.

See [LICENSE-GPL](LICENSE-GPL) for the full GPLv3 license text.

## Commercial Use

For commercial use, including but not limited to:
- Using this software in a commercial product or service
- Using this software to generate revenue
- Using this software in a business environment without releasing source code
- Removing or modifying the attribution requirements

You must obtain a commercial license from South City Computer.

See [LICENSE-COMMERCIAL](LICENSE-COMMERCIAL) for commercial licensing terms.

## Which License Do I Need?

| Use Case | License Required |
|----------|------------------|
| Personal website | GPLv3 (free) |
| Open source project | GPLv3 (free) |
| Educational/learning | GPLv3 (free) |
| Non-profit organization | GPLv3 (free) |
| Commercial website | Commercial License |
| SaaS product | Commercial License |
| Selling to clients | Commercial License |
| Closed-source derivative | Commercial License |

